Too many thanks to be given to all the people that came together to make this show happen. And to everyone who came out for the openings!
~
Jenn @parlorgallery for giving up her beautiful space, so Ben and I could load over 80 pieces into the empty space and quickly let it take shape over 36hrs
~ 
@keely__angel for her beautiful pieces in the show, keeping us sane, organized and on track throughout 🙏
~
and Ben @farmhaus___ for the friendship and vision to pull all of the artists together and make it happen for a short period of time. Oh, and those beautiful handmade frames. The perfect compliment to these pieces 🙏 
~
If your on the Jersey shore, stop by @parlorgallery. Ben will greet you with a smile. Show is up for another week and all pieces are for sale(some sold)
